data.description: Have you been looking for the right place to build a detached workshop garage with 200 AMP service on a separate power meter? Then look no further! We have a 3100+/-SQFT heated/cooled garage with three garage doors large enough to store your camper, plenty of space to work on your vehicle, and two additional rooms/offices with 12 to 16-foot ceilings! Also, a 20X20 wired building for additional storage & a three-car detached carport. The beautiful, well-maintained home has a 13X19 living room w/gas log precast stone fireplace and a 23X23 bonus/game room. Do you love to have barbeques and family functions? You will enjoy the 20X40 pergola with the eight-person hot tub. SITUATED ON THREE ACRES! All are thirty minutes from Burlington & Triad and 15 minutes from Danville. BE SURE TO CHECK OUT THE MATTERPORT LINK WALK THROUGH THE HOUSE AND SHOP ONLINE!  DON'T MISS THIS ONE! FHA, USDA & VA APPROVED! Home has always been used as 3BR home but septic permit is for 2BR.
